  "prompt": "Where can I buy raw egg noodles/ramen in Manipal? Is there a brand?",
  "response": "In Manipal, you can find raw egg noodles or ramen at local grocery stores or specialty shops that sell Asian ingredients. Some recommended places to check include:\n\n1. **Local grocery stores** - Stores like Koshy's may carry various types of noodles, including fresh or dried egg noodles.\n2. **Asian supermarkets** - If there are any Asian grocery stores in the area, they are likely to have a selection of ramen and egg noodles.\n3. **Online shopping** - Platforms like Amazon or other local e-commerce sites might have brands like Nissin, Shin Ramyeon, or other specialty brands that offer egg noodles or ramen.\n\nAlways check product descriptions to confirm the type of noodles you're looking for! If you're unsure, visiting these stores in person can help you find exactly what you need.",
